    "description": "Uniform Next Co., Ltd. engages in the sale of uniforms to companies, stores, and individuals in Japan. The company offers restaurant uniforms, such as aprons, shirts, pants, T-shirts, and polo shirts, as well as Japanese-style uniforms, such as sakumu uniforms; and kitchen and cooking uniforms, such as cook and lab coats. It also offers work uniforms, such as long-sleeved and short-sleeved blousons, shirts, cargo pants, tsunagi, winter clothing, safety shoes, air-conditioned clothing, rain gear, and other workwear for construction, ironwork, electrical engineering, agricultural work, manufacturing plants, transportation warehouses, and delivery sales. The company's medical uniforms include nurse and doctor uniforms, such as nurse wear, dresses, scrubs, examination gowns, and casey lab coats; and office uniforms include jackets, skirts, overblouses, shirts, cut-and-sew, vests, scarves, skirts, culottes, pants, dresses, and accessories for reception, information, customer service, sales, field work, office work, and medical office work, such as hospitals and nursing homes, and companions. It offers its products through mail order and door-to-door sales. Uniform Next Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1994 and is headquartered in Fukui, Japan."
